A(\mathbb T)
A(\mathbb T):= \{f:\mathbb T \to \mathbb R : \hat{f}\in \ell^{1}(\mathbb Z), \  \text {that is,} \  \sum_{n\in \mathbb Z} |\hat{f}(n)| < \infty \}.
||f||= \sum_{n\in \mathbb Z} |\hat{f}(n)| < \infty; \ \text {for} \ f\in A(\mathbb T). 
